29095251292615412694.Text: I told Kaye I have given up trying to find the Silver Staff of Shaming that belonged to Linus Iulus. He was disappointed, and told me not to come back for at least a day. He told me to decide whether I was serious about serving the Imperial cult before I ask him again for a shrine sergeant mission.

19062117927811766.Text: Imperial Cult: The Silver Staff of Shaming
